I really don't have anything to say about this map. It's small map made for GG gametype. This map has 32 spawns, so it's full of action when there are 16 players on both teams.

I wasn't even so sure if I have to make spawns like these to make it to work in GG, but after testing a little bit - it should be totally fine. I also tried my best with adding default textures - I am not the greatest man with adding textures around the place.

Special thanks to Vmx for giving some advice.

Anyways, **happy fraggin'**.
